    },
    {
      "end": 124.91999816894531,
      "text": "You ain't even gleaming when I see that",
      "start": 122.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 127.77999877929688,
      "text": "Just sit there shut the f**k up",
      "start": 124.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 131.6199951171875,
      "text": "Don't say you're this you're that",
      "start": 129.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 133.44000244140625,
      "text": "You're just a muck up",
      "start": 131.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 134.82000732421875,
      "text": "Push a cup",
      "start": 133.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 137.36000061035156,
      "text": "No one gives a f**k if you were there",
      "start": 134.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 140.16000366210938,
      "text": "Amen if I'm pissing on you to put fire out",
      "start": 137.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 144.33999633789062,
      "text": "Just a bitch bitch don't be that way",
      "start": 141.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 146.4600067138672,
      "text": "Listen here shut the f**k up",
      "start": 144.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 149,
      "text": "The kindness and love that he shows you",
      "start": 146.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 150.66000366210938,
      "text": "Scares you and pushes you away",
      "start": 149
    },
    {
      "end": 154.25999450683594,
      "text": "It's all you need when you don't know what to think",
      "start": 151.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 155.66000366210938,
      "text": "So what do you do?",
      "start": 154.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 157.6199951171875,
      "text": "You bring your friend back into a thug",
      "start": 155.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 159.24000549316406,
      "text": "Cause that's all you ever know",
      "start": 157.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 162.75999450683594,
      "text": "You get it and you're fighting with you",
      "start": 159.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 165.77999877929688,
      "text": "Only this time you realize you better decide again",
      "start": 162.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 169.17999267578125,
      "text": "Cause you're on the floor bleeding from his ass",
      "start": 165.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 171.17999267578125,
      "text": "He hit you again",
      "start": 169.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 173.5,
      "text": "You're lying in your puddle of your own blood",
      "start": 171.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 175.4199981689453,
      "text": "Thinking why this again?",
      "start": 173.5
    },
    {
      "end": 176.9600067138672,
      "text": "Shut the f**k up",
      "start": 176.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 179.44000244140625,
      "text": "What did I do to deserve this?",
      "start": 176.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 180.9600067138672,
      "text": "But it's too late",
      "start": 179.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 183.3800048828125,
      "text": "You would've known this is your last breath",
      "start": 180.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 186.1199951171875,
      "text": "He said he's gonna take his gun and put it to your head",
      "start": 183.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 188.3000030517578,
      "text": "He just shut the f**k up",
      "start": 186.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 190.77999877929688,
      "text": "You beg for your life and he says it's too late",
      "start": 188.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 196.89999389648438,
      "text": "Are you even sitting there crying on the couch?",
      "start": 194.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 198.4600067138672,
      "text": "Like come the f**k on",
      "start": 196.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 200.77999877929688,
      "text": "Get the f**k out of here",
      "start": 199.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 201.77999877929688,
      "text": "Don't be a f**king b**ch",
      "start": 200.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 203.74000549316406,
      "text": "You're the last guys in the world",
      "start": 201.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 205.9600067138672,
      "text": "Don't be quick to judge",
